{
  "stem": "21308.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were very skilled.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We could say, oh, that's a plowed field or it's grass or it's cultivated.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you knew as soon as in the dark when he got into that sort of land where you were and you used various methods of staking your time out.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, you-- you'd map this route out and then you told the chop who you were working to the route and then you would mark key post-- key points on this route.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then when you reckoned you were there, you would ask for a round to be thought on, shall we say it was a code named Shark, you would call for Shark one round and they'd fire one round.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you'd say, well, that should be over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that's how you could keep pace with where you were going.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it was always exciting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were all supremely confident because we knew that there weren't better gunners anywhere than us and we knew the kommandos were superb at night fighting.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The-- they-- it was an elite force and we all trusted each other.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you'd carry hard rations yourselves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] You would sleep where you were, this is in battle.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You'd get a few minutes whenever you could.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you had dug in, well, you'd be in a slit trench.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But because of the excitement, the adrenaline rush-- it runs very fast, very fast-- and the-- we would ensure that hot food got to us, particularly in bad weather.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the thing which we learned in Scotland when we were training for Arctic warfare, that men who've got empty stomachs get much colder than men who haven't.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they're not so good soldiers.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
